metadata.description:
Losing Grip is an important track for me. It started back in Winter of 2021 when the UK was in Lockdown.

We can start to lose grip of reality at points but it's important to hold on. This song for me symbols no matter what happening in life, keep going and don't let go.

Excited to bring this to Sound as my genesis drop. It's been a goal to release here since I found the platform in Feb 2022 and it's finally happening.

Proud to be dropping and hope you enjoy the music. Golden Egg winner is welcome to a 1-1 online call with me and I'll send you a t-shirt/vinyl, or both if you want.

Thanks for collecting.

Acutek
